<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Json_Server (ZF1) currently only allows errors in range(-32099, -32000).  For ZFv2, the implementation should be changed to adhere to the spec:
* Error code can be any integer
* Codes in range(-32700,-32000) are reserved for protocol implementation</p>

<p>See: ZF-11991 for more information.  Thanks to [~448191] for raising the ZFv1 issue.</p>

